The '''Biblioteca Nacional [[Pedro Henríquez Ureña]]''' (in [[English language|English]]: ''Pedro Henríquez Ureña National Library'') is the national library of the [[Dominican Republic]]. It is the legal deposit and copyright library for the Dominican Republic. It was inaugurated on February 28, 1971.

